scene.message:
Toro: Demons are scary, but I{nl}
think this is a chance.{waitkey}{clearbox}If I show Ayase a good side{nl}
of me, she might just{wait_fr:32}{nl}
f-fall for {wait_fr:21}me{wait_fr:21}, right?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kenta Yokouchi{nl}
Nicknamed Toro. Loves to eat.{nl}
Strong, but timid at heart.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Toro's kinda scary{nl}
right now. His eyes have{nl}
gone all funny.{waitkey}{clearbox}Word is he's still hanging{nl}
around Ayase like always.{waitkey}{clearbox}Guys like that get scary{nl}
when they brood too much.{waitkey}{ret}
